library(devtools)
library(engsoccerdata)
library(dplyr)
per=0

spain %>%
  filter(tier == 1) -> pl


pl %>% group_by(Season) %>% summarise(count=n())->counts
index=cumsum(counts)

half<-function(Begin,End){
 
  halfdf<-pl[(Begin:((Begin+End)/2)),]
  return(halfdf)
}

b=1
for (i in c(1:86)) {
  
  
  End=index[i,2]
  e=as.integer(End[1,1])
  df=half(b,e)
  
  rbind(
    df %>%
      select(Season, team = home, opp = visitor, GF = hgoal, GA = vgoal),
    df %>%
      select(Season, team = visitor, opp = home, GF = vgoal, GA = hgoal)
  ) %>% mutate(GD = GF-GA) %>% 
    group_by(team) %>% 
    summarize(GP = n(),
              goalsF = sum(GF),
              goalsA = sum(GA),
              goaldif = sum(GD),
              W = sum(GD>0),
              D = sum(GD==0),
              L = sum(GD<0)
    ) %>% 
    mutate(score = W*3 + D) %>%
    arrange(desc(score)) ->final
    champ_season=final$team[which.max(final$score)]
    
    tot=pl[b:e,]
    rbind(
      tot %>%
        select(Season, team = home, opp = visitor, GF = hgoal, GA = vgoal),
      tot %>%
        select(Season, team = visitor, opp = home, GF = vgoal, GA = hgoal)
    ) %>% mutate(GD = GF-GA) %>% 
      group_by(team) %>% 
      summarize(GP = n(),
                goalsF = sum(GF),
                goalsA = sum(GA),
                goaldif = sum(GD),
                W = sum(GD>0),
                D = sum(GD==0),
                L = sum(GD<0)
      ) %>% 
      mutate(score = W*3 + D) %>%
      arrange(desc(score)) ->tot_final
    champ_totseason=tot_final$team[which.max(tot_final$score)]
    
    if(champ_season==champ_totseason){
      per=per+1
    }
    
  
  
  Begin=index[i,2]+1
  b=as.integer(Begin[1,1])
}
  

cat("in what percent of seasons the half season champion became the season champion:",100*per/86)
## in what percent of seasons the half season champion became the season champion: 53.48837

library(devtools)
library(engsoccerdata)
library(dplyr)

spain %>%
  filter(tier == 1) -> pl
pl %>% select(Date,Season,home,visitor,hgoal,vgoal)->pl
seasons=pl %>% select(Season) %>% distinct()

for (i in c(1:86)) {
  data=pl %>% filter(Season==seasons[i,1])
  d=dim(data)[1] %>% as.integer()
  
  teams=data %>% select(team=home) %>% distinct()
  zero=matrix(0,nrow =dim(teams)[1] %>% as.integer() ,ncol = 1)
  final=data.frame(name=teams,score=zero)
  
  
  for (j in c(1:d)) {
    local=data[j,]
    if(local$hgoal==local$vgoal){
      final$score[which(local$home==final$team)]=local$hgoal+final$score[which(local$home==final$team)]
      final$score[which(local$visitor==final$team)]=local$vgoal+final$score[which(local$visitor==final$team)]
    }
    
    if(local$hgoal>local$vgoal){
      final$score[which(local$home==final$team)]=3*local$hgoal+final$score[which(local$home==final$team)]
      
    }
    
    if(local$hgoal<local$vgoal){
      
      final$score[which(local$visitor==final$team)]=3*local$vgoal+final$score[which(local$visitor==final$team)]
    }
    
    
    
    final %>% mutate(rank=rank(-score) %>% as.integer()) %>% arrange(desc(-rank))->final
    
    gap=final[1,2]-final[2,2]
    time=d-j
    
    if(gap>3*time & time>38){
      print(final[1,1])
      print(time)
      print(local$Date)
      
    }
   
      
      
    } 
    
  }

library(devtools)
library(engsoccerdata)
library(dplyr)

spain %>%
  filter(tier == 1) -> pl


pl %>% arrange(-desc(Date))->plsort
plsort %>% group_by(Season,Date) %>%
  mutate(equal=ifelse(hgoal==vgoal,1,0),homewin=ifelse(hgoal>vgoal,1,0),homeloose=ifelse(vgoal>hgoal,1,0),visitorwin=ifelse(hgoal<vgoal,1,0),visitorloose=ifelse(vgoal<hgoal,1,0))->stat
stat %>% select(Season,Date,team=home,win=homewin,loose=homeloose,Equal=equal)->temp1
stat %>% select(Season,Date,team=visitor,win=visitorwin,loose=visitorloose,Equal=equal)->temp2
data=rbind(temp1,temp2)
data %>% arrange(Season,team)->teamdata
teamdata %>% group_by(Season,team) %>% summarise(totalwin=sum(win))->tot_win
tot_win_max=max(tot_win$totalwin) 
teamdata %>% group_by(Season,team) %>% summarise(totalloose=sum(loose))->tot_loose
tot_loose_max=max(tot_loose$totalloose) 
teamdata %>% group_by(Season,team) %>% summarise(totalequal=sum(Equal))->tot_equal
tot_equal_max=max(tot_equal$totalequal) 

teamdata$tavali_w=0
for (i in c(1:tot_win_max)) {
  teamdata$tavali_w=ifelse(teamdata$win==lag(teamdata$win) & teamdata$win==1 &teamdata$team==lag(teamdata$team),lag(teamdata$tavali_w)+1,0)  
}
teamdata %>% group_by(team) %>% summarise(Season=Season[which.max(tavali_w)],tavali_win=max(tavali_w)+1)->final
cat("longest win:",final$team[which.max(final$tavali_win)] )
## longest win: FC Barcelona
teamdata$tavali_l=0
for (i in c(1:tot_loose_max)) {
  
  teamdata$tavali_l=ifelse(teamdata$loose==lag(teamdata$loose) & teamdata$loose==1 & teamdata$team==lag(teamdata$team),lag(teamdata$tavali_l)+1,0)
}
teamdata %>% group_by(team) %>% summarise(Season=Season[which.max(tavali_l)],tavali_loose=max(tavali_l)+1)->final2
cat("longest loose:",final2$team[which.max(final2$tavali_loose)] )
## longest loose: AD Almeria
teamdata$tavali_e=0
for (i in c(1:tot_equal_max)) {
  teamdata$tavali_e=ifelse(teamdata$Equal==lag(teamdata$Equal) & teamdata$Equal==1 &teamdata$team==lag(teamdata$team),lag(teamdata$tavali_e)+1,0)  
}
teamdata %>% group_by(team) %>% summarise(Season=Season[which.max(tavali_e)],tavali_equal=max(tavali_e)+1)->final3
cat("longest equal:",final3$team[which.max(final3$tavali_equal)] )
## longest equal: Hercules CF
